data.description: TRULY A MUST SEE HOME IN A BEAUTIFUL COASTAL CONDOMINIUM COMMUNITY! Located in Harbor Walk, a great relaxed community with tranquil walking trails, community clubhouse & pool, and beautiful views of Little Creek (also known as "Pretty Lake") where you can occasionally see some dolphins! Located just minutes from East Beach, JEB Little Creek-Fort Story Base, Interstates, Shopping and Restaurants! Owners have been living in this condo since it was built in 2015 and truly kept it well maintained. Great open floor plan with tall ceilings! Durable granite countertops and tall Kitchen cabinets, great for storage. Primary bedroom has an elegant tray ceiling and surrounding windows that bring in all the natural daylight. Primary bathroom features two closets, dual sinks, and a standing shower. Condo also comes with a lovely screened porch. Harbor Walk also features a marina with available boat slips, and limited access kayak and paddleboard launch. Schedule your showing today!
